---
title: Falafel Stuffed Peppers with Couscous
description: A quick falafel crumble makes a wonderful filling for Middle Eastern-inspired stuffed peppers. This veggie dinner will definitely fill you up, with a dollop of hummus providing a deliciously creamy finish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/poivrons-farcis-de-falafels-08a9e77f.jpg
